According to " <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">China Securities News</ENAMEX> " reporting , the <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">65 billion</ENAMEX> financial bonds issued <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">this year</ENAMEX> by <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the National Development Bank</ENAMEX> , are not within the scope of this <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">year</ENAMEX> 's domestic securities issuance plan , moreover , they are brought into this <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">year</ENAMEX> 's credit scope of specialized banks , and also included in the fixed capital investment plan drafted by <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the State Planning Commission</ENAMEX> .
