It does not have any source of funds of its own , and is not for profit .
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">The Development Bank</ENAMEX> has many capital sources and channels .
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">Firstly</ENAMEX> , it has registered capital of <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">50 billion yuan</ENAMEX> allocated from national finance .
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">Secondly</ENAMEX> , it issues bonds to financial institutions .
